Class DescargaSvc

com.sicomsa.dmt.svc.DescargaSvc
All Implemented Interfaces:
Service<DescargaResponse,String>
public class DescargaSvc extends AbstractGenericSvc<DescargaResponse,String>
Extends AbstractGenericSvc to provide a concrete implementation of the WS defined for downloading specific packages:
"https://cfdidescargamasiva.clouda.sat.gob.mx/DescargaMasivaService.svc"

This class has concrete methods to create a download package request; sign, and send it to the web service. Then parse the response to provide a DescargaResponse with methods to query the response.

If the package was downloaded then DescargaResponse will have the package and you can access it with the method getEncodedPackage().

The encoded package will be a String extracted from the SOAPMessage received from the web service; to save it you should decode it:

      byte[] decoded = java.util.Base64.getDecoder().decode(encodedPackage);
